Description: aiojson
        =======
        
        Simple json template verifier for ``aiohttp``
        
        Usage
        -----
        
        Simple example:
        
        .. code-block:: python
        
            from aiohttp import JsonTemplate
        
        
            @JsonTemplate({
                "messages": [{
                    "id": int,
                    "text": str
            }])
            async def received_message(request, validated_data):
                pass
        
Platform: UNKNOWN
